HEADWORD: Strockle
<hw>Stroc"kle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Glass Manuf.)</fld>
<def>A shovel with a turned-up edge, for frit, sand, etc.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>strocal</asp>, <asp>strocle</asp>,
<asp>strokal</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

